00:46:33.020 --> 00:46:38.900
And we all live inside our disciplines and
we all live inside a limited sphere of

00:46:38.900 --> 00:46:44.870
knowledge. But we are all pessimistic it
would seem because to a person in the

00:46:44.870 --> 00:46:50.330
sustainability arena, each of us would
say, within our limited perception that

00:46:50.330 --> 00:46:56.240
we've never seen problems quite of this
scale. And more than that, nobody is

00:46:56.240 --> 00:47:03.810
listening. Those are big problems, and so
