00:47:03.810 --> 00:47:08.290
back from the structured knowledge that
we've tried to relate to you and think

00:47:08.290 --> 00:47:14.200
more philosophically. We are thinking
about the next century but I'd like to

00:47:14.200 --> 00:47:21.310
point out the tremendous problems in the
last century that our grandparents and

00:47:21.310 --> 00:47:29.230
parents solved. They solved, they grew,
the century started with terrible mass

00:47:29.230 --> 00:47:35.471
warfare. Conflicts between dictators, much
