00:47:35.471 --> 00:47:38.871
unprecedented much reduced.

00:47:40.800 --> 00:47:52.620
Colonialism, gone to a large extent. And
finally, we began to solve the fundamental

00:47:52.620 --> 00:47:58.510
problem of the third world. And we now
have set, as a civilization the forbidding

00:47:58.510 --> 00:48:04.420
on the way to a decent way of life. So
these are enormous transformations in

00:48:04.420 --> 00:48:10.600
