count on the creativity of human beings,

00:48:16.350 --> 00:48:21.610
this enormously competent culture that we
all live in, I count on increased

00:48:21.610 --> 00:48:31.200
connectivity in that culture. And that
connectivity is sustained and propagated

00:48:31.200 --> 00:48:36.920
by our concern for each other and the
ethical concern that we will develop for

00:48:36.920 --> 00:48:45.130
ourselves as a civilization and for our
climate environment as a whole. So with

00:48:45.130 --> 00:48:52.140
